<div class="uw-text-block">
    <p>Welcome to our International Student FAQ! With such a large international student population in our Statistics department we know that students often have specific questions. Below, we have compiled some of the most common questions we are asked so that hopefully you can receive quick answers. We are happy to have an appointment with you if your situation is more complex or not addressed by this list.</p>
<p>Undergraduate students: schedule with a <a href="https://stat.wisc.edu/undergraduate-advising/">Statistics</a> or <a href="https://stat.wisc.edu/undergraduate-data-science-studies/">Data Science</a> major advisor.</p>
<p>Graduate students: contact your Graduate Program Coordinator, listed in <a href="https://guide.wisc.edu/">Guide</a>.</p>
</div>
