    <h3 class="uw-accordion-header">
      How many credits do I need to enroll in?     </h3>

    <div class="uw-accordion-panel -uw-accordion-is-hidden">
      <div class="uw-accordion-panel-inner uw-clearfix">
        <p>According to I<a href="https://iss.wisc.edu/students/current-students/f1-information/full-time-enrollment/">SS enrollment policy</a>, to maintain your visa status, graduate students must enroll in a minimum of 8 credits each fall and spring semester.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  
    <h3 class="uw-accordion-header">
      Can I enroll part time in my last semester?     </h3>

    <div class="uw-accordion-panel -uw-accordion-is-hidden">
      <div class="uw-accordion-panel-inner uw-clearfix">
        <p>According to <a href="https://iss.wisc.edu/students/current-students/reduced-course-load/">ISS RCL policy,</a> students in their final semester of study are eligible to enroll part time in their last semester if they need less than a full-time course load to complete their program of study.</p>
      </div>
